<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>نِصَابًا، فَلاَ قَطْعَ فِيمَا دُونَهُ عِنْدَ جُمْهُورِ الْفُقَهَاءِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَلَكِنَّهُمُ اخْتَلَفُوا فِي تَحْدِيدِ مِقْدَارِ هَذَا النِّصَابِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَالتَّفْصِيل فِي مُصْطَلَحِ <span class="c2">(سَرِقَة ف ٣٢ وَمَا بَعْدَهَا)</span> .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>نَصَارَى<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرْ:</span> أَهْل الْكِتَابِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>نُصْرَةٌ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرْ:</span> عَاقِلَةٌ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>